In the{pig unit}of this Farm there are some 300 sows. They and their progeny are kept in very good conditions with a controlled enviorment.
The farm yard{manure}and slurry wastes form a valuable manure particularly for the potato crop and reduce the need for artificial fertilisers. {*****}
Much of the area around High and Low Risby has been subjected to{mining {subsidence}from old mine workings. Many of the farm tracks and areas of land have been fenced off as unsafe for the general public.
